org.apache.solr.core

Interface JmxMonitoredMap.JmxAugmentedSolrInfoMBean

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SolrInfoMBean
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SolrFieldCacheMBean
    Enclosing class:
    JmxMonitoredMap<K,V>

    public static interface JmxMonitoredMap.JmxAugmentedSolrInfoMBean
extends SolrInfoMBean
    SolrInfoMBean that provides JMX-specific statistics. Used, for example, if generating full statistics is expensive; the expensive statistics can be generated normally for use with the web ui, while an abbreviated version are generated for period jmx use.
